        "orario": "16:35",
        "timestamp": 1773329730,
        "contenuto_esteso": "The Israeli military said on Thursday that Hezbollah had fired around 200 rockets at Israel the night beforeFRANCE 24's Olivia Bizot reports from one of the buildings in Tel Aviv that was hit during the very first days of the war by an Iranian missile. Since then, \"a sense of normality has returned to the streets\", she explains."
